creator: Go Outdoors Iowa, LLC
descriptionHtml:
Do you hunt or fish in Iowa? This application is for you. Made available by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources (IADNR) and GoOutdoorsIowa.com, this free application contains a variety of useful tools and information including:

- Store your license on your phone and sync recent purchases
- Access to hunting and fishing regulations, season and bag limit information, and fishing information
- Access to Iowa’s hunting and fishing licensing system
- Location based Sunrise/Sunset Timer and Moon Phases
- Online & Offline Harvest Registration
- plus Iowa Events & Maps

The application requires Internet access for some features. Let us know your ideas for improvements and future features.
descriptionShort: Official App of the Iowa Department of Natural Resources - GoOutdoorsIowa.com

And much more
